.TH CONV-ALIAS 1 "July 2026" "ConVigurator Manual"
.SH NAME
conv-alias \- validates and normalizes custom user-defined aliases.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B conv-alias
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B conv-alias
inspects user-defined shell profiles (.bashrc, .zshrc, config.fish) to identify non-compliant alias overrides and suggest standardized conv- prefixed naming alternatives.
.SH SEE ALSO
conv-shell(1)
